Package com.github.natanbc.lavadsp.distortion

Class DistortionPcmAudioFilter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.natanbc.lavadsp.ConverterPcmAudioFilter<DistortionConverter>
      • com.github.natanbc.lavadsp.distortion.DistortionPcmAudioFilter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.sedmelluq.discord.lavaplayer.filter.AudioFilter, com.sedmelluq.discord.lavaplayer.filter.FloatPcmAudioFilter
    public class DistortionPcmAudioFilter
extends ConverterPcmAudioFilter<DistortionConverter>
    Applies simple math to each sample. Base formula is 
     
 sampleSin = sinOffset + sin(sample * sinScale);
 sampleCos = cosOffset + cos(sample * cosScale);
 sampleTan = tanOffset + tan(sample * tanScale);
 sample = max(-1, min(1, offset + scale * (useSin ? sampleSin : 1) * (useCos ? sampleCos : 1) * (useTan ? sampleTan : 1)));
